&lt;p&gt;Not like a hoarder. (I suppose this is relative&amp;hellip;)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I don&amp;rsquo;t believe I have a &lt;em&gt;problem&lt;/em&gt; (Doesn&amp;rsquo;t everyone who has a problem say that? Or, could it be I have way too much stuff? I&amp;rsquo;ll have you know I sold 8 items on &lt;a href="https://reverb.com/" class="external-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Reverb.com&lt;/a&gt; !!)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I would say that if it&amp;rsquo;s a problem it started in earnest around 1984-85 when I got my 1st &amp;ldquo;real&amp;rdquo; &lt;a href="https://www.vintagesynth.com/yamaha/dx9" class="external-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;synthesizer&lt;/a&gt;. My stuff now is way &lt;em&gt;cooler&lt;/em&gt;, man. (Or, could it be that it&amp;rsquo;s only cool to me?)&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>